name: Comfortable Stay, not far from Downtown and Fenway
description:
Enjoy a relaxing stay in the historic community of Roxbury, Massachusetts! Within close proximity of many of the city's greatest tourist attractions!

The space
Single family house located across the street from Roxbury Community College and the Reggie Lewis Athletic center. 75 yards from Roxbury Crossing MBTA Station and 5 minute walk to Northeastern University. 10 minute subway ride to Downtown Boston

The Room itself includes:

Roku TV (Free Netflix)
Ceiling Fan
AC
Portable Space Heater
2 Lamps
Desk
Closet

Guest access
Guest's have access to a full kitchen, two bathrooms and a very comfortable living room area.
Kitchen also includes coffee maker, toaster, and a microwave.

Other things to note
Street Parking: Street cleaning on Tuesdays between 8 AM-12 Noon from April to November


**IMPORTANT NOTICE**

I can NOT accommodate early arrival
